snippet: The starting quarterbacks in the 1996 Fiesta Bowl, Tommie Frazier of Nebraska and Danny Wuerffel of Florida, were chosen for induction into the College Football Hall of Fame.
abstract: Tommie Frazier of Nebraska and Danny Wuerffel of Florida, starting quarterbacks in the 1996 Fiesta Bowl, are chosen for induction into the College Football Hall of Fame.
